metadata.name: Good Fortune & Prosperity
metadata.description:
An Illustration depicting a beautiful lady (fictional) as a manifestation of my own prayer for good fortune and prosperity. I view the Creator of this universe and the universe itself as something beautiful that is always looking after you and always listening to you. This could be your lucky charm too.

2D Hand painted 2400x3000 PX
Process https://sta.sh/0g407v74m9n
